title: 1970 U.S. in the Canadian 1941 neighborhood.
subtitle: The eBay list of a quarter that was said to have been wrapped in the back of a Canadian coin in 1941 sounds real, but the money may not appear in anybody's sofa pillows.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A bunch of quarters in the 1970s are worth a fortune, and mints have also been minted on the back of a Canadian currency of 1941.
